<codeline lineno="77"><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">##<sp/>@purpose<sp/>To<sp/>rotate<sp/>an<sp/>image<sp/>by<sp/>a<sp/>given<sp/>angle<sp/>with<sp/>automatic<sp/>bound<sp/>expansion,<sp/>preventing<sp/>corner<sp/>cropping<sp/>and<sp/>preserving<sp/>all<sp/>content<sp/>for<sp/>OCR.</highlight></codeline>
