<codeline lineno="153"><highlight class="normal"></highlight><highlight class="comment">##<sp/>@purpose<sp/>To<sp/>vertically<sp/>concatenate<sp/>a<sp/>list<sp/>of<sp/>PIL<sp/>images<sp/>into<sp/>a<sp/>single<sp/>combined<sp/>image,<sp/>preserving<sp/>the<sp/>maximum<sp/>width.</highlight></codeline>
